# FlickTrack - Your Ultimate Movie Companion 🎬🍿

![FlickTrack Icon](app/src/main/res/mipmap-xxhdpi/icon_app_round.webp)

Welcome to **FlickTrack**, your go-to mobile app for discovering, exploring, and keeping up-to-date with all your favorite movies! With **FlickTrack**, you can easily browse through a wide selection of films, get detailed information, and set release date reminders for your most anticipated titles!

## Features 🚀

- **Movie Discovery**: Browse a wide range of movies with ease.
- **Detailed Movie Info**: Get all the details you need about your favorite movies, including cast, plot, release date, and more.
- **Personalized Notifications**: Set custom alerts for upcoming movie releases so you never miss out!
- **Seamless User Experience**: Developed with **Clean Architecture** to ensure smooth performance and scalable growth.
- **Firebase Integration**: Save your preferences and track your favorite movies securely with Firebase.
- **User-friendly Interface**: Clean, intuitive design to ensure you have the best movie-watching experience!

## How It Works 🛠️

1. **API Integration**: FlickTrack fetches up-to-date movie data via API, bringing you the latest and greatest in cinema.
2. **Firebase Sync**: Your data is synced and stored with **Firebase**, keeping your preferences and favorite movies safe.
3. **Set Reminders**: Get notified on your phone whenever a movie you're interested in is about to hit theaters.
4. **Stay Updated**: FlickTrack keeps you in the loop, showing you the most recent movies and upcoming releases.

## Tech Stack 💻

- **Languages**: Java
- **Technologies**: Firebase, Native Android (Android Studio)
- **Architecture**: Clean Architecture
- **Database**: Firebase Realtime Database

